Name: Dream Within Dream (I)
Desc: After every attack launched by an ally, applies 1 stack of Memory Imprint to all allies. Allies in the Memory Imprint state deal <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> more DMG. This effect stacks up to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak></color> time(s). When Memory Imprint reaches max stacks, immediately regenerate <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> Energy for all allies. The Energy regenerated by this effect can exceed the target's Max Energy.\nRemove all Memory Imprints from all allies at the start of every wave or Cycle.
